\intbl \ql \b Background\b0 \line Stenden South Africa BV \'28Incorporated in the Netherlands\'29 previous known as  Educational Institute for\line Service Studies International \'28Pty\'29 Ltd. is  registered with the Department of Higher Education and Training as a private higher education provider and is accredited to offer a Bachelor of Commerce \'28Hospitality Management\'29.\line \line The Bachelor of Business Administration in Disaster Relief Management served at the Accreditation Committee Meeting of 05 and 06 October 2011 and it was not accredited for the following reasons\'3A \line 1. The formal curriculum appears to be at a Level 7\'2C with only WIL at Level 8 of the NQF. It is not clear that the assessment of WIL will be commensurate with Level 8.\line 2. According to the curriculum the course entails experiential training for which little evidence of possible contracts is presented. These experiential training facilities will need to be supported by contracts to be presented in evidence.\line \line The institution submitted a representation.\line \cell \pard 

